# Data files (don't commit large data)
# If you want to track specific small data files, use negative pattern:
# !data/small_file.json
data/*.csv.gz
data/*.parquet
data/*.xlsx
!data/readme.md
!data/LICENSE.txt
!data/clean/*.parquet
